{"tid":1723893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論]星期一至五黎明行動，星期六日富城行動","createTime":"2019-11-15T10:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T10:29:00.000Z","uid":33729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"741d175c402462b922cd45fe1582bbc11f3829f1","tid":1723893,"uid":33729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"星期一至五嘅黎明行動頗有成效，成功令半個香港經濟及交通癱瘓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但另一方面經過咗連續五日，相信唔少手足都開始攰，漸露疲態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一方面又要保持住士氣，一方面又要俾手足有充足嘅休息，暫時比較可行嘅方法就係展開<span style=\"color: red;\">「富城行動」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n富城，除咗代表支持返經常出現示威現場撐手足嘅城城，亦代表幫助呢個城市富有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以星期六日不論和勇，大家一齊18區商場和你Shop塞爆佢，周末當然係行商場放鬆，唔係都對唔住自己啦係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫襯啲咩罷買啲咩，相信大家都心裡有數，至於邊啲鋪頭到時心虛關門，唔關我地事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另一重點就係，亦都可以多幫襯黃色小店，始終相信呢幾日行動令佢地出現一定嘅困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎明係我地嘅主線，富城係我地嘅支線，無論邊個都好，最緊要都係各位手足嘅支持。<br />\n不分化，不割蓆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uE8gwSr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuE8gwSr.png&h=3cb8f5a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53cf52910a0b9b4e13bb82e5cf2a4eb7ad0cedcf","tid":1723893,"uid":33729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:12:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c963d855aa3c151e0e092db1553ffef54e60cbc","tid":1723893,"uid":33729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:25:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29e45e084b469bc579e5c8cdd0c423f0a5d944b","tid":1723893,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:29:00.000Z","msg":"not bad"}]}